            <h3 class="display-4">Overview</h3>
            <div style="width:1000px;height: 100px; float: left; font-size: large;">
                Many job searching platforms usually create hassles for job hunters. This includes but is not limited to
                requiring registration, not being user friendly
                or including a plethora of irrelevant information and so on. This effectively downgrades the experience
                of job hunters who always need to utilize their time efficiently.
                Leaving the task of interpreting requirements and benefits to the applicant is not optimal and may even
                affect the number or quality of people that are applying.
                Our goal is to provide the most up-to-date STEM job postings along with a central location where
                applicants and employers can search whether at a desk
                or on the go. A simple user-friendly database and interface will provide people a platform/market
                analysis to get back out into the industry and
                help businesses get back on their feet during or after the pandemic.
            </div>
